captions.text:
- SO, KAT DENNINGS, IT'S
BREAST CANCER AWARENESS MONTH.

ALL MONTH LONG WE'VE BEEN
RAISING MONEY HERE AT THE SHOW.

IT'S SOMETHING THAT'S VERY
PERSONAL TO YOU.

MY BEST FRIEND MY--
SINCE I WAS 14

AT 31, GOT DIAGNOSED WITH
TRIPLE NEGATIVE BREAST CANCER.

AND SHE--
HER SCANS HAVE COME BACK CLEAR

SHE'S DOING GREAT,
SO THIS IS VERY--

SO THE DUNK TANK WAS
A LITTLE TOO SCARY FOR YOU,
- ALL OF THIS IS COMING OFF.

- YEAH.
- MY WEAVE WILL FALL OUT.

- OH, WELL, WE...
- I MEAN, IT'S NOT GOOD.

- WE DON'T WANT TO SEE WHAT'S
UNDER THERE, SO LET'S...

- LET'S--LET'S NOT SEE
BEHIND THE CURTAIN.

- SO WE'RE NOT GONNA DO THAT TO
YOU, BUT YOU'LL HAVE 60 SECONDS

- YEP.
- IF YOU GET ALL 10 QUESTIONS
THEN NOTHING WILL HAPPEN TO YOU.

THAT MYSTERY BUCKET UP THERE
WILL DUNK SOMETHING.

IT--WHO KNOWS WHAT IT IS?
IT COULD BE WATER.

SO ALL MONTH LONG WE'VE BEEN
TEAMING UP WITH ULTA BEAUTY

TO RAISE AWARENESS FOR
BREAST CANCER RESEARCH.

YOU'RE GONNA BE A GOOD SPORT.
THEY'RE GONNA DONATE $10,000.

- GET--GET ON
THOSE LITTLE PADS THERE.

- STAY RIGHT THERE
ON THOSE PADS.

I MEAN, THAT WOULD BE CRAZY
IF WE WOULD DO THAT.

OR EVEN ANTS.
WHY WOULD WE DO THAT?
DO I GET GOGGLES OR SOMETHING?

TODAY'S QUESTIONS ARE
ALL ABOUT CATS,

AND SINCE YOU--I THOUGHT
YOU KNEW A LOT ABOUT THEM.

- YOU WERE WRONG.
- ALL RIGHT, 60 SECONDS

THE TIN MAN, THE SCARECROW,
AND WHAT BIG CAT

"CAT IN A HAT" IS
DR. SEUSS'S BOOK.

WHAT'S SOMETHING ELSE
YOU PUT ON YOUR HEAD?
MILLIE IS THE NAME OF YOUR CAT.

MELLIE IS THE NAME OF
THE FIRST LADY ON THE SHOW

THAT AIRS ON ABC
THURSDAY NIGHTS AT NINE.

IN "THE LION KING,"
HE BECOMES KING OF THE JUNGLE.

ANTONIO BANDERAS WAS
THE VOICE OF THIS CAT.

- THEN YOU'RE LOSING.
THE COUNTRY POP STAR HAS A CAT

NAMED AFTER A "LAW & ORDER: SVU"
CHARACTER ON--OLIVIA BENSON.

- AND THE CAT IN "BREAKFAST AT
TIFFANY'S" IS NAMED...?

- I DON'T KNOW.
LET'S DO THIS.

- ALSO A WINNER BECAUSE
THAT MEANS $10,000

FOR BREAST CANCER RESEARCH.
- OH. WHEW.

- THE SEASON PREMIER OF
"2 BROKE GIRLS"
